{"_id":"L1HlX8xTr8L1m4mM","name":"Hirnloser the Genius","type":"threat","img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","items":[{"_id":"9hUrX8lDPzVwARo6","name":"Hirnloser the Genius - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Hirnloser the Genius","source":"OZena the Suffering and Desperate","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>My mind has become infallible, and I can \ncalculate and check any variable in seconds. I have a strategy \nfor every situation.</p>","notes":"OZena the Suffering and Desperate - bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 241.","positive":"My mind has become infallible, and I can \ncalculate and check any variable in seconds. I have a strategy \nfor every situation.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Hirnloser the Genius","source":"OZena the Suffering and Desperate","category":"threat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781557624693,"modifiedTime":1781557624693,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}},{"_id":"GrexxrHhlQ6XB8XE","name":"Source Text","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/svg/scroll.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Hirnloser the Genius","source":"OZena the Suffering and Desperate","category":"threat"}},"system":{"description":"<p>– Main NPC (3 Wounds)\nDescriptor: My mind has become infallible, and I can \ncalculate and check any variable in seconds. I have a strategy \nfor every situation.\nAgenda: Solve any potential problems that plague my \nbenefactor Norman Henkle.</p>","notes":"OZena the Suffering and Desperate - bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 241.","owner":"Hirnloser the Genius","source":"OZena the Suffering and Desperate","category":"threat"},"sort":0,"ownersh